  "comment": "The OUTBACK350H features a powerful 350W white LED source with an impressive 69,703 lux output at 5m (3° beam angle) delivering exceptional brightness with a crisp 8,000K colour temperature. Versatile colour capabilities include dual colour wheels , plus CMY+CTO colour mixing for precise colour control. The dual rotating gobo wheels offer extensive pattern options with indexing and shaking functions for dynamic effects. Control options include 3 and 5 pin dmx as well as included WDMX capabilities. ",
